{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MrrRRDXv5tDeHC2GCCvAH5","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Story {{epic_num}}.{{story_num}}: {{story_title}}\n2\t\n3\tStatus: ready-for-dev\n4\t\n5\t<!-- Note: Validation is optional. Run validate-create-story for quality check before dev-story. -->\n6\t\n7\t## Story\n8\t\n9\tAs a {{role}},\n10\tI want {{action}},\n11\tso that {{benefit}}.\n12\t\n13\t## Acceptance Criteria\n14\t\n15\t1. [Add acceptance criteria from epics/PRD]\n16\t\n17\t## Tasks / Subtasks\n18\t\n19\t- [ ] Task 1 (AC: #)\n20\t  - [ ] Subtask 1.1\n21\t- [ ] Task 2 (AC: #)\n22\t  - [ ] Subtask 2.1\n23\t\n24\t## Dev Notes\n25\t\n26\t- Relevant architecture patterns and constraints\n27\t- Source tree components to touch\n28\t- Testing standards summary\n29\t\n30\t### Project Structure Notes\n31\t\n32\t- Alignment with unified project structure (paths, modules, naming)\n33\t- Detected conflicts or variances (with rationale)\n34\t\n35\t### References\n36\t\n37\t- Cite all technical details with source paths and sections, e.g. [Source: docs/<file>.md#Section]\n38\t\n39\t<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-START:story-verification -->\n40\t## Verification Requirements\n41\t\n42\t- [ ] Showboat proof document created (verification/<story-key>-proof.md)\n43\t- [ ] All acceptance criteria verified with real-world evidence via docker exec\n44\t- [ ] Test coverage meets target (100%)\n45\t\n46\t## Documentation Requirements\n47\t\n48\t- [ ] Relevant AGENTS.md files updated\n49\t- [ ] Exec-plan created in docs/exec-plans/active/<story-key>.md\n50\t\n51\t## Testing Requirements\n52\t\n53\t- [ ] Unit tests written for all new/changed code\n54\t- [ ] Coverage target: 100%\n55\t<!-- CODEHARNESS-PATCH-END:story-verification -->\n56\t\n57\t## Dev Agent Record\n58\t\n59\t### Agent Model Used\n60\t\n61\t{{agent_model_name_version}}\n62\t\n63\t### Debug Log References\n64\t\n65\t### Completion Notes List\n66\t\n67\t### File List\n68\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id